# ============================================================================
# Inventra POS — Frontend Environment Variables
# ============================================================================

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# API CONFIGURATION
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Backend API URL
# Development: http://localhost:5000/api
# Production: https://your-api-domain.com/api
#
# NOTE: If you want to run COMPLETELY OFFLINE (no backend at all):
#       DELETE or COMMENT OUT this line below
#       Frontend will auto-detect offline mode and use localStorage
#
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RUNNING MODES EXPLAINED:
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. ONLINE MODE (with backend API):
#    • Set: VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
#    • Data: Stored in MongoDB
#    • Auth: Real JWT tokens from backend
#    • Email: Password reset emails work
#    • Multiple users: Yes
#
# 2. OFFLINE MODE (no backend API):
#    • Delete or comment out: VITE_API_URL
#    • Data: Stored in browser localStorage (15-20MB limit)
#    • Auth: Demo accounts (hardcoded in AuthContext)
#    • Email: No password reset
#    • Multiple users: No (single local user)
#    • Offline accounts:
#      - Email: super@inventra.com | Password: SuperAdmin@123
#      - Email: admin@inventra.com | Password: Admin@1234
#      - Email: manager@inventra.com | Password: Manager@123
#      - Email: sales@inventra.com | Password: Sales@1234
#      - Email: accounts@inventra.com | Password: Accounts@123
#
# 3. ELECTRON DESKTOP APP (offline desktop):
#    • Delete: VITE_API_URL
#    • Data: Stored in SQLite (persistent, no size limit)
#    • Auth: Demo accounts
#    • Perfect for: Shops with unreliable internet
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
